Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.70,0:02:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个好厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.20,0:02:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉重的列车正缓缓浮向夜空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.30,0:02:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}超能渡边无论是名字还是相貌都在恶搞本动画原案渡边博
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.30,0:02:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如超能渡边预告的那样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.40,0:02:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他用双手神力正吊起列车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.60,0:02:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浮起来 浮起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.60,0:02:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是闹剧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.40,0:02:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.40,0:02:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 这是最近的话题人物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.20,0:02:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.20,0:02:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,视觉系灵能力者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.10,0:02:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名叫基路 多 隆菲尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.40,0:02:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中途杀入节目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.50,0:02:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来揭穿你的谎言了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.50,0:02:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基路大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.00,0:02:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎 怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.60,0:02:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没人告诉我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.48,0:02:46.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}请打败他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.80,0:02:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这 这怎可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.70,0:02:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是超能渡边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.70,0:02:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果敢的接受了基路的挑战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.30,0:03:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.10,0:03:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 住手啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.20,0:03:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要想停下 就承认自己撒了谎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.50,0:03:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快停下啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.50,0:03:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不承认就会坠入地狱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.90,0:03:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.10,0:03:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么做让小姐知道了怎么办啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.10,0:03:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不让她知道就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.80,0:03:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话是没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.10,0:03:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是露馅了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.40,0:03:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要说我们之前劝你很多次哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.00,0:03:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.90,0:03:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.30,0:04:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.70,0:04:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,字:灵能力少年基路 多 隆菲尔向超能渡边下挑战书
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.10,0:04:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超能渡边先生 怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.00,0:04:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他现在身处另一个世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.90,0:04:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个戏也做的太夸张了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.20,0:04:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不相信吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.60,0:04:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.00,0:04:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.40,0:04:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还亏得你相信地狱少女的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.20,0:04:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是电视的声音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.10,0:04:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 仅仅把人送往地狱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.50,0:04:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想并不是解决问题的办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.40,0:04:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以这种事情不能再继续下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.20,0:04:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 突然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.00,0:04:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.80,0:04:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来有什么缘由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.50,0:04:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饶了我 饶了我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.90,0:04:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是真正的超能力者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.50,0:04:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是骗术 饶了我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.60,0:04:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样 感觉到她的反应了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.10,0:04:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的能和她相通吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.40,0:04:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.30,0:04:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能看见地狱少女看见的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.80,0:05:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看见的东西她也应该能看见才对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.20,0:05:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相通 什么意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.20,0:05:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.80,0:05:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在看的电视不知道她看到没
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.50,0:05:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.40,0:05:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了 回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.20,0:05:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.00,0:05:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底对超能渡边做了什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.30,0:05:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他见识了一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.70,0:05:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地狱哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.50,0:05:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真敢吹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.40,0:05:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是 这个假冒灵能力者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.00,0:05:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿部小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.60,0:05:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下周起的节目怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.80,0:05:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那还用说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.60,0:05:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改和那个男孩签约
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.10,0:05:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么下周起请多关照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.30,0:05:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼此彼此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.00,0:05:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.40,0:05:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一边去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.80,0:05:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他肯定很怨恨吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.10,0:05:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此 让他再怨恨些吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.20,0:05:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道地狱少女吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.40,0:05:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是听过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.20,0:06:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她和我一样散发着真实的气息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.20,0:06:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定不是这个世上的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.90,0:06:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过那样的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.30,0:06:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.80,0:06:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基路 多 隆菲尔对地狱少女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.00,0:06:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿部小姐不想看吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.50,0:06:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想看 绝对要看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.80,0:06:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是到哪里去联系她呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.50,0:06:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联系的话就拜托渡边先生吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.20,0:06:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 是呢 好主意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.40,0:06:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上写进计划里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.60,0:06:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地狱少女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.10,0:06:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别以为在网上有名气 就自以为了不起了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.10,0:06:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.20,0:06:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么说小姐也是不知不觉就向那个女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.70,0:06:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.60,0:06:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说这边可以向那边传达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.40,0:06:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而那边却不能向这边传达呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.60,0:07:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 刚才那个男的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.10,0:07:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 这么相信就够了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.50,0:07:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 响了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.30,0:07:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身败名裂了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.10,0:07:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种对决不接受就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.40,0:07:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我干吗还在这里擦靴子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.90,0:07:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.10,0:07:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 真想再多赚点才死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.00,0:07:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 渡边先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.50,0:07:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.80,0:07:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是阿部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.20,0:07:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后还要请你关照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.10,0:07:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超能力的事尽管找我超能渡边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.80,0:08:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托您的福这次节目反响强烈啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.20,0:08:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定很郁闷吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.30,0:08:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样 想不想向基路反击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.40,0:08:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我干我干 包在我身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.30,0:08:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那太好了 那明天21点摄影棚见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.80,0:08:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包在我身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.30,0:08:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机会 等着瞧吧 基路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.20,0:08:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次我要把你煮了 看我怎么煮你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.30,0:08:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布景这样做就可以了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.50,0:08:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,节目安排得怎么样了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.60,0:08:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间太紧了 现场直播是不可能了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.90,0:08:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过第二天的特别节目中播出的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.60,0:08:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那他呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.40,0:08:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,21点过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.10,0:08:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他本人为了报复昨天的事干劲十足呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.40,0:08:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当知道那是骗他的时候怨恨就会更深了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.10,0:09:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使这么做也不知能不能联系上地狱少女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.10,0:09:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.20,0:09:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经吩咐工作人员干得彻底些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.40,0:09:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那太感谢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.10,0:09:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 和地狱少女取得联系后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.10,0:09:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多长时间才来呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.90,0:09:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.90,0:09:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是坐电车来呢 还是汽车呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.90,0:09:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.20,0:09:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您是哪位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.80,0:09:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.20,0:09:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些事情想问您
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.70,0:09:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,采访的话能不能通过局里的宣传部呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.60,0:09:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能去地狱是真的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.10,0:09:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.60,0:09:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么时候的事呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.80,0:09:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小时侯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.00,0:09:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 采访请通过宣传部预约
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.00,0:09:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 您知道地狱少女吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.50,0:09:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么呢 我们什么都不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.50,0:09:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有话想你替我转告地狱少女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.00,0:10:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了 不知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.40,0:10:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.90,0:10:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手吧 谁也不会得到幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.50,0:10:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,报仇是没有意义的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.60,0:10:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,报仇是没有意义的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.70,0:10:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.40,0:10:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.10,0:10:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是伪善吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.90,0:10:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 您说的没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.70,0:10:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过即使脑子里明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.70,0:10:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心灵深处却无论如何也想粉碎对手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.60,0:10:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人就是这样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.40,0:10:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.30,0:10:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.70,0:10:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么您怎么样呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.10,0:10:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.50,0:11:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做了什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.80,0:11:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才是您的太太吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.20,0:11:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话我会转告的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.50,0:11:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我想是不会得到回应了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.80,0:11:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是真家伙吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.00,0:11:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经12点了 要我等到什么时候呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.50,0:11:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 大概还要好些时间吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.60,0:11:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基路先生的工作堆了很多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.40,0:11:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么只顾着他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.30,0:11:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没我这场反击大戏无法开演吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.10,0:11:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和预想的一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.40,0:11:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.70,0:11:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基路先生说 想报仇的只是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.00,0:11:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他希望更强的人当对手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.20,0:12:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.30,0:12:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.60,0:12:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么差不多了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.60,0:12:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说 是基路先生的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.40,0:12:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那东西给他吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.20,0:12:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡边先生肚子饿了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.10,0:12:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 住手啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.10,0:12:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是基路先生请你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.10,0:12:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想烫死我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.00,0:12:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死 基路这家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.00,0:12:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想耍我到什么地步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.70,0:12:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一会儿要狠狠教训他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.20,0:12:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电脑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.30,0:12:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地狱通信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.50,0:12:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是怪小姐呢还是怪那家伙的女儿呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.40,0:12:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,声音太大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.20,0:12:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许不只是其中任一方的原因呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.10,0:12:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.40,0:13:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人之间也许存在着什么接点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.10,0:13:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有委托 跟我来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.30,0:13:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.60,0:13:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你在呼唤我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.20,0:13:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是阎魔爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.10,0:13:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小爱 你真可爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.50,0:13:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请收下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.80,0:13:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个要怎么用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.10,0:13:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你若真的要消除怨恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.60,0:13:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将这红线解开即可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.00,0:13:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解开绳线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.40,0:13:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就和我正式缔结了契约
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.40,0:13:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.50,0:13:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怨恨的人将立刻坠入地狱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.20,0:13:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么马上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.30,0:13:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.10,0:14:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怨恨若已消除
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.70,0:14:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自身亦将付出代价
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.50,0:14:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害人终害己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.90,0:14:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缔结契约后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.60,0:14:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的灵魂亦将坠入地狱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.40,0:14:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过那是你死之后的事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.00,0:14:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.50,0:14:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕是当然的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.10,0:14:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.10,0:14:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.70,0:14:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我事先没听说啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.60,0:14:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.90,0:14:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很高兴见到你 阎魔爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.20,0:14:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.90,0:14:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.50,0:14:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是基路 多 隆菲尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.20,0:14:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意思是来自地狱的基路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.90,0:14:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能让真正的地狱少女大驾光临实属荣幸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.70,0:14:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基路 你竟敢利用我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.50,0:14:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.10,0:15:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烫 烫 烫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.00,0:15:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三流艺人吃萝卜真是太合适了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.40,0:15:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在 我来说明一下这次的计划
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.90,0:15:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今在电视上最受关注的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.60,0:15:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和网络上最受关注的你之间的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.00,0:15:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赌上生死的地狱对决
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.50,0:15:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即将播出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.70,0:15:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被人设了陷阱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.40,0:15:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 怎么可能赢得了小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.30,0:15:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太高兴了这才有意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.50,0:15:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 基路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.40,0:15:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在跟谁说话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.30,0:15:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这怎么做节目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.60,0:15:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么啊 不是在这里吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.00,0:15:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.20,0:15:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.30,0:16:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么荒谬的节目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.40,0:16:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我怎么向上面解释啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.80,0:16:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢了 那么你们也
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.40,0:16:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.30,0:16:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用的 你们解不开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.50,0:16:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于只剩下我们了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.60,0:16:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对 有个叫柴田的记者有话转告你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.50,0:16:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说报仇不是好事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.70,0:16:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是充满正义感呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.80,0:16:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么喜欢装腔作势的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.30,0:16:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就做点坏事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.60,0:16:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到那些被审判的人待的地狱里去采访不就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.00,0:16:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过对他来说是勉强了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.30,0:16:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他不像我这样能从地狱回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.60,0:17:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 我是与生俱来的超能力者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.90,0:17:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现此事的父母因为害怕把我杀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.90,0:17:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我从地狱回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.80,0:17:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.80,0:17:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来之后首先把我的亲生父母送下了地狱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.30,0:17:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什 什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.00,0:17:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是年幼时随意使用能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.00,0:17:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令周围一片混乱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.90,0:17:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父母没办法才这么做的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.30,0:17:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等长大一些后也许可以理解父母的所为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.10,0:17:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我还是动手了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.10,0:17:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全没有证据的完美杀人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.10,0:17:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把一家人都虐杀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.70,0:17:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并不打算将仇恨正当化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.50,0:17:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但因为这能力我吃尽了苦头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.80,0:18:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也应该理解我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.60,0:18:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.90,0:18:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把别人送下地狱是因为无法控制自己的仇恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.00,0:18:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能明白的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.10,0:18:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是你的话应该明白吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.10,0:18:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.50,0:18:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说点什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.30,0:18:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.40,0:18:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险啊 小爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.10,0:18:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.10,0:18:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想想办法啊 轮入道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.40,0:18:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要解开绳子我就有办法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.60,0:18:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你似乎为了别人再把坏人送往地狱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.50,0:18:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只是伪善
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.20,0:18:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你拥有那么强大的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.10,0:18:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不为了自己使用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.00,0:18:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衣服变的破破烂烂呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.60,0:18:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在不忍心就这样送你下地狱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.10,0:18:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我让你换上新的衣服吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.50,0:19:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺合身啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.50,0:19:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在是挺合身啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.90,0:19:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么该说永别了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.60,0:19:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.70,0:19:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.80,0:19:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们好好祭奠她吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.60,0:19:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.20,0:19:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.80,0:19:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.90,0:19:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.30,0:19:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么让那家伙为所欲为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.90,0:19:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在想事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.50,0:19:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这 不可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.20,0:19:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐 好好回敬他一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.40,0:20:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绳子还没解开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.30,0:20:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是这样 而且小姐的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.90,0:20:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎样都无所谓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.20,0:20:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.80,0:20:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你被这样羞辱之后就打算回去了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.20,0:20:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么让我来解开吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.70,0:20:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要解开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.20,0:20:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解开了你也要下地狱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.80,0:20:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是现在不解开绳子迟早被你干掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.60,0:20:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拜托她为我复仇 你不可能放过我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.10,0:20:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我放过你 真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.20,0:20:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.70,0:20:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地狱的恐怖是难以想象的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.30,0:20:42.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不可能承受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.10,0:20:44.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别把我当傻子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.70,0:20:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看三流艺人的决心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.30,0:20:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怨 恨 已 闻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.70,0:21:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 叫你们住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.80,0:21:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 妈妈 老师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.50,0:21:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让它们不要再复仇了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.50,0:21:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷失于黑暗的可悲之影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.30,0:21:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤害鄙视他人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.80,0:21:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉溺于罪恶的孽魂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.60,0:21:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来死一次吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.60,0:21:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是又一次吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.70,0:21:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是地狱啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.20,0:21:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次就让你赢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.10,0:21:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是无论送我下几次地狱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.10,0:21:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都会活过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.50,0:22:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你再分胜负
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.10,0:22:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此怨此恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.80,0:22:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将流向地狱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.30,0:22:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于得救了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.50,0:22:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱 有委托
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:38.50,0:22:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.80,0:23:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君之怨恨 愿为消之
