Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:46.30,0:24:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可他却一开始就
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:49.30,0:24:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿望是
